high_descs: Turn left and go towards the door ahead, but turn right before reaching it, then right again to the white table before the kitchen area.
Pick up the potato from the table.
Turn and go towards the kitchen area, to the microwave on the counter.
Use the microwave on the potato and remove it.
Turn around from the microwave towards the sink.
Place the potato on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved potato on a kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn left and turn right move towards the dining table.
Pick the potato from the dining table.
Turn left and turn right move towards the microwave.
Place the potato inside the microwave, pick the potato from the microwave.
Turn right move towards the sink.
Place the potato on the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the potato on the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the dining table by turning right.
Pick the potato from the dining table.
Turn around and head to the microwave on your right.
Place the potato in the microwave and pick it back after heating.
Place the potato on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the potato on the sink by heating it in the microwave oven.
